  ],
  "remarks": "Xiamen Limbach Aviation Engine Co., Ltd (Xiamen Limbach) is a Chinese company producing L550 series engines for drones. Xiamen Limbach Aviation Engine Co., Ltd has delivered such components to IEMZ Kupol, a subsidiary of Russian state-owned arms company Almaz-Antey, which subsequently were used for manufacturing long-range attack drones of the type Garpiya-3 (G3) for use in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Those deliveries were made through other entities registered in the People’s Republic of China, notably Redlepus TSK Vektor Industrial (Shenzhen) Co., Ltd and Juhang Aviation Technology Shenzhen Co. Ltd.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}